\cf0 This plug-in adds a "Set Desktop Picture" action that can act on individual image files or folders or remote URLs. For folders, the desktop picture will be chosen from that folder. The time interval for updating and whether the images will be chosen sequentially or randomly are taken from the last-used settings in the Desktop & Screen Saver Preference Pane. \
