\f1\b \cf0 Warnings
\f0\b0 \
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\ql\qnatural
\cf0 Using this plugin while the Desktop & Screen Saver Preference Pane is open may lead to unintended side-effects. These are believed to be limited to an unwanted reversion to a previous desktop picture setting when closing the preference pane, but could be as severe as corrupting the desktop picture preferences. If this happens, please move or delete ~/Library/Preferences/com.apple.desktop.plist.\
\
As of version 1.4.5, images from URLs are downloaded into ~/Library/Application Support/Quicksilver/Caches/Desktop Picture Action". Images are never cleaned up from this directory, so if you frequently use URLs to set your desktop picture, this directory may become large. Mac OS X may require that the currently-chosen image remain in this directory, so properly and safely pruning this directory's contents may prove difficult. \
